          "evidence_text_excerpt": "d Elite \u00ae * Mastercard \u00ae* . *109\nWhat is the required minimum balance for Blue Rewards Chequing Account? You don\u2019t need to keep a minimum balance in the account as long as you pay the monthly plan fee of $17.95. Plus, you can get\u202f500 Bonus Points\u202fevery month you maintain a daily balance of $4,000 or more in your chequing account. *106",
          "anchor_type": "section",
          "anchor_value": "what-is-a-blue-rewards-chequing-account",
