        {
          "field_name": "minimum_balance",
          "candidate_value": "17.95",
          "value_type": "decimal",
          "confidence": 0.88,
          "extraction_method": "heuristic_money",
          "source_document_id": "src-bmo-html-d77b7bcf92826785",
          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-c7fe3c918181b544",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-d4693f8f552f1c91",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What is the required minimum balance for Blue Rewards Chequing Account?\nYou don\u2019t need to keep a minimum balance in the account as long as you pay the monthly plan fee of $17.95. Plus, you can get\u202f500 Bonus Points\u202fevery month you maintain a daily balance of $4,000 or more in your chequing account. *106\nHow many transactions do you get with the Blue Rewards Chequing Account? With the Blue Rewards\u202fChequing Account, you get unlimited transactions *52 per month. When you move money out of your account \u2013 like an ATM withdrawal, bill payment or pre-authorized payment \u2013 that counts as a transaction. Money coming into your account \u2013 like payroll direct deposits or cash deposits at an ATM \u2013 don\u2019t count as transactions.",
          "anchor_type": "section",
          "anchor_value": "what-is-the-required-minimum-balance-for-blue-rewards-chequing-account",
          "page_no": null,
          "chunk_index": 21,
