        },
        {
          "field_name": "eligibility_text",
          "candidate_value": "A Blue Rewards Chequing Account is a bank account that allows you to earn Blue Points on eligible transactions you make with the account",
          "value_type": "string",
          "confidence": 0.55,
          "extraction_method": "heuristic_eligibility_text",
          "source_document_id": "src-bmo-html-d77b7bcf92826785",
          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-c7fe3c918181b544",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-3c3b25bf1c3b2e24",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Blue Rewards Chequing Account FAQs\nWhat is a Blue Rewards Chequing Account? A Blue Rewards Chequing Account is a bank account that allows you to earn Blue Points on eligible transactions you make with the account. The amount of Blue Points you earn per transaction depends on the terms and conditions of the Blue Rewards Chequing Account, as well as any offer or promotions related to the account. For example, this account lets you earn 2x the Points for every $2 in eligible grocery, wholesale club, EV Electric vehicle \u200b charging and gas purchases, and 1 Point for every $2 in purchases everywhere else. *9 You can also get 500 Bonus Points every month you maintain a daily balance of $4,000 or more in your chequing account, plus another $500 Bonus Points every month when you also have a BMO Blue Rewards World Elite \u00ae * Mastercard \u00ae* . *109",
          "anchor_type": "section",
          "anchor_value": "blue-rewards-chequing-account-faqs",
          "page_no": null,
          "chunk_index": 18,
          "field_metadata": {
            "retrieval_mode": "metadata-only",
            "matched_keywords": [
              "can",
              "eligible"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "field_name": "application_method",
          "candidate_value": "How do I open a Blue Rewards Chequing Account online?",
          "value_type": "string",
          "confidence": 0.78,
          "extraction_method": "heuristic_application_method",
          "source_document_id": "src-bmo-html-d77b7bcf92826785",
          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-c7fe3c918181b544",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-d91528587e1fb210",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "How do I open a Blue Rewards Chequing Account online?\nYou can open an Blue Rewards\u202fChequing Account online . You don\u2019t need an existing BMO chequing or savings account to apply for a Blue Rewards\u202fChequing Account.\nYou can also apply for the account in person\u202fat your nearest branch .\nHow do I link my existing Blue Rewards account to my Blue Rewards Chequing Account? When you open a Blue Rewards Chequing Account, you\u2019ll be asked to link your existing Blue Rewards Member Number to the chequing account. That way, you can continue to earn Blue Points without opening a new one.",
          "anchor_type": "section",
          "anchor_value": "how-do-i-open-a-blue-rewards-chequing-account-online",
          "page_no": null,
          "chunk_index": 23,
          "field_metadata": {
            "retrieval_mode": "metadata-only",
            "matched_keywords": [
              "account",
              "apply",
              "branch",
              "online",
              "open"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "field_name": "unlimited_transactions_flag",
          "candidate_value": true,
          "value_type": "boolean",
          "confidence": 0.59,
          "extraction_method": "heuristic_flag",
          "source_document_id": "src-bmo-html-d77b7bcf92826785",
          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-c7fe3c918181b544",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-570836e70a1a30df",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "How many transactions do you get with the Blue Rewards Chequing Account?\nWith the Blue Rewards\u202fChequing Account, you get unlimited transactions *52 per month. When you move money out of your account \u2013 like an ATM withdrawal, bill payment or pre-authorized payment \u2013 that counts as a transaction. Money coming into your account \u2013 like payroll direct deposits or cash deposits at an ATM \u2013 don\u2019t count as transactions.\nHow do I open a Blue Rewards Chequing Account online? You can open an Blue Rewards\u202fChequing Account online . You don\u2019t need an existing BMO chequing or savings account to apply for a Blue Rewards\u202fChequing Account. You can also apply for the account in person\u202fat your nearest branch .",
