          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Legal\nFootnote 1 details 1 Standard daily Points usage limits and terms and conditions apply for in-store partner redemptions and eGift e-Gift \u200b\u200b Cards. Other forms of redemptions are subject to separate terms, conditions and redemption rates. See bluerewards.ca/value for full details.",
