          "candidate_value": "Save on taxes \u2013 Purchase a GIC in an RRSP or TFSA for a number of tax benefits.",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-13e363593c147d59",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Guaranteed Investment Certificates ( GIC s)\nWhat is a GIC ? It\u2019s a safe, secure investment that can suit all kinds of financial goals. A GIC protects your principal, so no matter what happens with the market, you\u2019ll never lose your initial investment. \u00a0Plus, all of our GIC s are CDIC-insured footnote 1 1 .\nStay safe and secure \u2013 Your initial investment is 100% guaranteed.\nEnjoy a versatile investment \u2013 Choose a GIC to suit your needs.\nSave on taxes \u2013 Purchase a GIC in an RRSP or TFSA for a number of tax benefits.",
