          "candidate_value": "Dollar Premium Rate Savings Account online?",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-2b6afea7cee9d218",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Can I open a U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings Account online?\nYes, you can. If you\u2019re an existing BMO customer, you can sign in to Online Banking to add the Premium Rate Savings Account.\nIf you\u2019re new to BMO , you\u2019ll need to get a chequing account with us first *100 before you can add the U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings Account.\nWhat are the fees for the U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings Account? The good news is that the U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings account can be added to your Chequing Plan and you pay only one monthly fee. If you don\u2019t want a chequing account but just want a U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings account, you\u2019ll have to visit a branch. If you already have a Chequing Plan, you can open a U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings account online in BMO Online Banking or the BMO Mobile app. Plan and transaction fees on your chequing account will vary depending on the Plan you",
