          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-64d71329dce80567",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-954c4297ec8bc8ca",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Save on bank fees\nWant to save money on bank fees? We\u2019ll show you how!\nPrefer to avoid paying fees for moving your money? We\u2019ve got you covered.\nGet unlimited monthly transactions *52 with the Premium Chequing Account , the Performance Chequing Account and the Blue Rewards Chequing Account\nWant to keep tabs on your transactions? View your account history through BMO Online Banking or BMO Mobile Banking\nATM fees can add up quickly. The good news is that we can help you avoid them.\nOver 2,150 BMO ATM in Canada means that there are plenty of convenient places to bank on the go\nEnjoy unlimited non- BMO ATM withdrawals worldwide *53 with the Premium Plan Chequing Account\nTake advantage of online services like Interac e-Transfer \u00ae\u2021 footnote registered section transactions to send money to family and friends\nAvoid the stress and inconvenience of NSF fees by applying for Overdraft Protection",
