          "candidate_value": "Open an Account In a TFSA, interest earned from your GICs is tax-free.",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-933e10d7a43b5e6f",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Open an Account\nIn a TFSA, interest earned from your GICs is \n tax-free. legal disclaimer 4\nIn an RRSP, interest earned from your GICs is not \n taxed legal disclaimer 5 until it is withdrawn.\nIn an RESP, interest earned from your GICs is not taxed \n until it is withdrawn by the student.\nWhen you hold a GIC in a non-registered investment \n account, any interest your GIC earns is subject to tax \n and must be added to your taxable income.\nFor Existing Clients:\nOpen Online\nNot a client: Call 1-800-463-3863\nFor Existing Clients:\nOpen Online\nNot a client: Call 1-800-463-3863\nFor Existing Clients:\nOpen Online\nNot a client: Call 1-800-463-3863\nFor Existing Clients:\nBook an Appointment\nNot a client: Call 1-800-463-3863\nOpen Online\nOnce your account is opened, you can make a contribution \n to purchase the GICs you want to hold in it.\nView Legal Disclaimers Hide Legal Disclaimers\nBase Level from",
