          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Guaranteed-Return GICs\nWith Guaranteed-Return GICs, your interest rate is guaranteed, so you don't need to worry \n \n about changes in the markets or economy.\nNon-Redeemable GIC\nTerm to Maturity\nInterest Paid at Maturity * , Semi-Annually, Annually or at Maturity (Compounded Annually)\nInterest Paid Monthly *\n30 - 59 days\n-\n60 - 89 days\n-\n90 - 179 days\n-\n180 - 269 days\n-\n270 - 364 days\n-\n1 year\n1.5 years\n2 years\n3 years\n4 years\n5 years\n7 years\n10 years\nInterest rates are subject to change without notice at any time. Rates shown are calculated on a per annum basis. * For terms less than 1 year, interest is only paid at maturity.\nRedeemable GIC\nTerm to Maturity\nInterest Paid at Maturity * , Semi-Annually, Annually or at Maturity (Compounded Annually)\nInterest Paid Monthly *\n30 - 59 days\n-\n60 - 89 days\n-\n90 - 179 days\n-\n180 - 269 days\n-\n270 - 364 days\n-\n1 year\n1.5 years\n2 years\n3 years\n4",
