          "candidate_value": "Legal 4 As of May 26, 2025, new and existing Preferred Package for Students and Youth account holders who have or open a Scotia iTRADE\u00ae account will receive a waiver of commission on all eligible commissionable trades (up to $9.99 CAD/USD per transaction) (the \u201cWaiver\u201d)",
