          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Banking Services\nIf you have a Scotiabank Personal Bank Account, these changes may impact you.\nCURRENT\nNEW\nWAYS TO SAVE\nNSF\nEFFECTIVE MARCH 9, 2026\nCheque or other debit item returned for insufficient funds (NSF)\n$48\n$10 This fee will not apply if the difference between the account balance and the funds needed when we receive a payment item is $10 or less. It will also not be charged more than once within two business days per account.\n$10\nThis fee will not apply if the difference between the account balance and the funds needed when we receive a payment item is $10 or less. It will also not be charged more than once within two business days per account.\nEnrol in Overdraft Protection and Info Alerts to avoid NSF fees.\nStop Payment\nEFFECTIVE MARCH 20, 2026\nFee\nComplete: $12.50 Incomplete: $20\nComplete: $12.50\nIncomplete: $20\nAssisted 2 : $30.00 Self-Serve 3 : $0.00\nAssisted 2 : $30.00",
