        {
          "field_name": "application_method",
          "candidate_value": "As of March 31, 2026, once you turn 25 , if you aren\u2019t a student anymore, we\u2019ll automatically change your account to a regular Preferred Package and the monthly account fee will apply.",
          "value_type": "string",
          "confidence": 0.66,
          "extraction_method": "heuristic_application_method",
          "source_document_id": "src-scotia-html-00d5a2001b2f2e5d",
          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-fff1ca407167e7c1",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-bec5bf69ab693a9e",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What happens to my Preferred Package for Students and Youth after I turn 25?\nAs of March 31, 2026, once you turn 25\u00a0, if you aren\u2019t a student anymore, we\u2019ll automatically change your account to a regular Preferred Package and the monthly account fee will apply. If you\u2019re still a student, you can keep your Preferred Package for Students and Youth by providing valid proof of enrolment like:\nA student card with an expiry date\nA letter from your school\nA course timetable for the current academic year\nEither way, your debit card number, account number, and your online banking and mobile banking details will stay the same.",
