          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-58eee7c32139f55f",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Have questions?\nMeet with a Scotia advisor Use our online tool to schedule your visit.\nGive us a call We\u2019re ready to give you advice.\nEligible for CDIC Insurance\nRegular Interest is calculated by applying the Regular Interest Rate to your daily closing balance and is paid monthly. Refer to Current Rates Page for current Regular Interest Rates, which are subject to change.",
