        {
          "field_name": "withdrawal_limit_text",
          "candidate_value": "If you conduct a debit transaction before a Premium Period end-date, you\u2019ll still earn Regular Interest but will forgo any accrued Premium Interest.",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-104b0ab7d700490f",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Can I withdraw money from my Momentum PLUS Savings Account before the Premium Period end-date?\nYes, you can withdraw your money any time. If you conduct a debit transaction before a Premium Period end-date, you\u2019ll still earn Regular Interest but will forgo any accrued Premium Interest.\nA new Premium Period of the same duration will automatically re-start the same day with your remaining balance. If you have more than one Premium Period, only the Premium Period you withdraw from will be affected.",
